{"tid":679213,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"單程機票係咪真係會入唔到境 / 直頭唔比上機?","createTime":"2018-05-26T16:23:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T17:37:12.000Z","uid":85084,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4d02f7d6d50b7a274825c606c0f67ced53074efd","tid":679213,"uid":85084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T16:23:41.000Z","msg":"小弟打算7月由芬蘭經德國去希臘 玩幾個月<br />\n<br />\n但始終係幾個月之後既事又要途經幾個國家好難預幾時會返香港 <br />\n可能唔會係希臘做終點會玩多幾個國家<br />\n又或者可能未去到希臘就唔夠錢要中途返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以機票都係諗住買單程<br />\n但上網睇好似話買單程機票會有機會唔比上機 或者 去到會唔比入境?<br />\n<br />\n同埋就算芬蘭入到 由芬蘭入其他國家又會唔會比人攔住?<br />\n<br />\n有冇有經驗既巴絲可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6208cee191cfa05919216b59d58ed78c708266","tid":679213,"uid":151324,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T16:27:06.000Z","msg":"你自己都識講唔夠錢 佢就係驚你無錢買走果程"},{"pid":"b2cfdc8ebb4ec4e05774475b4f2d1382745484a2","tid":679213,"uid":85084,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8e6208cee191cfa05919216b59d58ed78c708266","tid":679213,"uid":151324,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T16:27:06.000Z","msg":"你自己都識講唔夠錢 佢就係驚你無錢買走果程"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T16:29:05.000Z","msg":"姐係如果有一定數量現金show比佢睇就無問題?"},{"pid":"b377d711a7e9be9270d3ebb34b513a5e654da703","tid":679213,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T16:30:48.000Z","msg":"邊有人問你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話唔係經飛機返去咪得"},{"pid":"e156776fd91c25fb663cb21ddb73658a14e4d389","tid":679213,"uid":99642,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2cfdc8ebb4ec4e05774475b4f2d1382745484a2","tid":679213,"uid":85084,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8e6208cee191cfa05919216b59d58ed78c708266","tid":679213,"uid":151324,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T16:27:06.000Z","msg":"你自己都識講唔夠錢 佢就